ActNational Capital Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of ELEANOR HENDERSON MOHAMMED of Charlottetown, Prince Edward Island, to be a member of the Board of Directors of the National Capital Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Lisa M. MacDonald, whose term has expired.
